Title: Casing the Camp
Description: Now we take you to camp. You see what Boss Whiskerlash do. Put on bug disguise when we close to camp. Let me do talking.
CompletionText: Can no let this camp stand. Too much to lose for kobold and earthen.
RewardText: You see what Glumtooth Gang do? Even have earthen prisoner!

Objectives.Text: Put on the Flawless Bug Disguise
